name: L’amour est compliqué
description:
Cliff Blank | Community Pool Drop

"My heart spins, my pulse races. The thief that you are, you occupied my life like a sudden carjacking. At every turn in every direction, you certainly didn't follow the rules of love. And it feels like an exhilarating car chase through the streets of the City of Light. There's no going back to my pedestrian life."
